    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.89.72083.figures12-19>
    dc:description "Figures 12 - 19. Panurgine male sternum seven 12 Halopanurgus baldocki 13 Avpanurgus flavofasciatus 14 Camptopoeum (Epimethea) variegatum 15 Flavipanurgus flavus 16 Flavipanurgus kastiliensis 17 Panurgus (Panurgus) calcaratus 18 Panurgus (Panurgus) dentipes 19 Panurgus (Pachycephalopanurgus) farinosus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/650543" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.89.72083.figures4-11>
    dc:description "Figures 4 - 11. Panurgine male genitalia 4 Halopanurgus baldocki 5 Avpanurgus flavofasciatus 6 Camptopoeum (Camptopoeum) frontale 7 Camptopoeum (Epimethea) variegatum 8 Flavipanurgus flavus 9 Flavipanurgus venustus 10 Flavipanurgus kastiliensis 11 Panurgus (Panurgus) calcaratus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/650542" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.89.72083.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Male genital capsule of Halopanurgus baldocki, with arrow indicating the apical part of the gonocoxa which is produced into a strong triangular point." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/650541" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.89.72083.figures31-32>
    dc:description "Figures 31 - 32. Flavipanurgus male genitalia 31 Flavipanurgus granadensis 32 Flavipanurgus merceti." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/650546" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.89.72083.figures28-29>
    dc:description "Figures 28 - 29. Halopanurgus baldocki comb. nov. profile 28 female 29 male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/650545" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.89.72083.figures20-27>
    dc:description "Figures 20 - 27. Panurgine faces 20 Halopanurgus baldocki comb. nov. male 21 Avpanurgus flavofasciatus male 22 Halopanurgus fuzetus comb. nov. female 23 Flavipanurgus granadensis female 24 Flavipanurgus kastiliensis male 25 Simpanurgus phyllopodus male, including 26 male antennae and 27 male fore tarsi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/650544" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

